Chweet Module
=============

Chweet is *"Post to Twitter"* Module developed to work with Chyrp version 2.2 and above.

Chweet (after enabling) tweets every new published posts to Twitter through the OAuth protocol. Thus, there's no need to enter username/password combination in order to submit a tweet. All you have to do is, authorize the module (app) to your account in Twitter and you'll be all set and ready to rock'n'roll.